sequenceDiagram
  participant FE as Frontend/Caller Service
  participant GW as NGINX
  participant SVC as Target Service
  participant AUTH as user-service /api/auth/verify

  FE->>GW: API request with Authorization: Bearer JWT
  GW->>SVC: forward request
  SVC->>AUTH: POST /api/auth/verify
  AUTH->>AUTH: validate JWT signature + claims
  alt token valid
    AUTH-->>SVC: 200 { userId, role }
    SVC->>SVC: proceed domain logic
    SVC-->>FE: success response
  else token invalid/expired
    AUTH-->>SVC: 401/403
    SVC-->>FE: unauthorized/forbidden
  end
